screen.drawLine(3, 6, 3, h-6) --Left side line screen.drawTriangleF(3, (h-6)-Z, 10, (h-9)-Z, 10, (h-3)-Z)
screen.drawLine(27, h/2, 38, h/2) --hoz line screen.drawLine(w/2, 27, w/2, 38) --vert line screen.drawTextBox(32, 3, 30, 7, string.format("%.0fm", RANGE), 1, 0)
if IR then screen.drawTextBox(12, (h/2)-3, 12, 7, "IR", 0, 0) screen.drawRect(11, (h/2)-4, 12, 8) end
end

function onTick() GPSX = input.getNumber(17) GPSY = input.getNumber(18) zoom = input.getNumber(19) MAPX = input.getNumber(20) MAPY = input.getNumber(21) WPX8 = input.getNumber(2) WPY8 = input.getNumber(1) WPX7 = input.getNumber(4) WPY7 = input.getNumber(3) WPX6 = input.getNumber(6) WPY6 = input.getNumber(5) WPX5 = input.getNumber(8) WPY5 = input.getNumber(7) WPX4 = input.getNumber(10) WPY4 = input.getNumber(9) WPX3 = input.getNumber(12) WPY3 = input.getNumber(11) WPX2 = input.getNumber(14) WPY2 = input.getNumber(13) WPX1 = input.getNumber(16) WPY1 = input.getNumber(15)
WPA1 = input.getBool(1) WPA2 = input.getBool(2) WPA3 = input.getBool(3) WPA4 = input.getBool(4) WPA5 = input.getBool(5) WPA6 = input.getBool(6) WPA7 = input.getBool(7) WPA8 = input.getBool(8)
WPNUM = input.getNumber(22)
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 100) screen.drawTextBox(46, 57, 20, 7,string.format("%.0fwp", WPNUM), 0, -1) screen.setColor(100, 0, 0) CPX, CPY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, GPSX, GPSY) WP1PX, WP1PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX1, WPY1) WP2PX, WP2PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX2, WPY2) WP3PX, WP3PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX3, WPY3) WP4PX, WP4PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX4, WPY4) WP5PX, WP5PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX5, WPY5) WP6PX, WP6PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX6, WPY6) WP7PX, WP7PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX7, WPY7) WP8PX, WP8PY = map.mapToScreen(MAPX, MAPY, zoom, w, h, WPX8, WPY8)
screen.drawCircleF(CPX, CPY, 2) if WPA1 then screen.drawLine(CPX, CPY, WP1PX, WP1PY) end if WPA2 then screen.drawLine(WP1PX, WP1PY, WP2PX, WP2PY) end if WPA3 then screen.drawLine(WP2PX, WP2PY, WP3PX, WP3PY) end if WPA4 then screen.drawLine(WP3PX, WP3PY, WP4PX, WP4PY) end if WPA5 then screen.drawLine(WP4PX, WP4PY, WP5PX, WP5PY) end if WPA6 then screen.drawLine(WP5PX, WP5PY, WP6PX, WP6PY) end if WPA7 then screen.drawLine(WP6PX, WP6PY, WP7PX, WP7PY) end if WPA8 then screen.drawLine(WP7PX, WP7PY, WP8PX, WP8PY) end end

-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() X = input.getNumber(10) Y = input.getNumber(11) MAPX = input.getNumber(12) MAPY = input.getNumber(13)
inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
Zoom = input.getNumber(9)
-- Check if the player is pressing the rectangle at (10, 10) with width and height of 20px isPressingRectangle = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 1, 2, 5, 5) isPressingRectangle2 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 1, 8, 5, 5) isPressingRectangle3 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 30, 1, 5, 5) isPressingRectangle4 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 30, 58, 5, 5) isPressingRectangle5 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 1, 30, 5, 5) isPressingRectangle6 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 58, 30, 5, 5) isPressingRectangle7 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 57, 2, 5, 5)
-- Set the composite output, on/off channel 1 output.setBool(1, isPressingRectangle) output.setBool(2, isPressingRectangle2) output.setBool(3, isPressingRectangle3) --UP output.setBool(4, isPressingRectangle4) --DOWN output.setBool(5, isPressingRectangle5) --LEFT output.setBool(6, isPressingRectangle6) --RIGHT output.setBool(7, isPressingRectangle7) --RESET end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() W = screen.getWidth() H = screen.getHeight()
screen.drawMap(MAPX, MAPY, Zoom) if isPressingRectangle then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(1, 2, 5, 5) if isPressingRectangle2 then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(1, 8, 5, 5) if isPressingRectangle3 then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(30, 1, 5, 5) --TOP if isPressingRectangle4 then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(30, 58, 5, 5) --BOTTOM if isPressingRectangle5 then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(1, 30, 5, 5) --LEFT if isPressingRectangle6 then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(58, 30, 5, 5) --RIGHT if isPressingRectangle7 then screen.setColor(0, 150, 0, 100) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50, 100) end screen.drawRectF(57, 2, 5, 5) --RESET
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 100) screen.drawTextBox(2, 2, 5, 5, "+", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(2, 8, 5, 5, "-", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(31, 1, 5, 5, "U", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(31, 58, 5, 5, "D", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(2, 30, 5, 5, "<", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(59, 30, 5, 5, ">", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(58, 2, 5, 5, "R", 0, 0)
end

object.script: function onTick() s=screen mc=math.cos ms=math.sin mp=math.pi ma=math.abs mq=math.sqrt iB=input.getBool iN=input.getNumber isPressed=iB(1) inputX=iN(3) inputY=iN(4) zoom=iN(5) gpsX=iN(6) gpsY=iN(7) a=(iN(8)*(-1))+0.25 ra=iN(9)*(-1) rd=iN(10) tn=iN(12) gpsToggle=iB(13) rTarget=iB(14) rToggle=iB(15) keepWaypoint=iB(16) rClean=iB(17) wd=(iN(11)-iN(8))*2*mp T = 100 end function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight() if isPressed then onTouch(1) elseif touchscreen and gpsToggle then onTouch(0) end if touchscreen and isPressed and laststate~=(inputX+inputY)then mapX, mapY=map.screenToMap(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,inputX,inputY) laststate=(inputX+inputY) waypointX,waypointY=mapX,mapY elseif not touchscreen then mapX=gpsX mapY=gpsY end s.drawMap(mapX,mapY,zoom) if not touchscreen then if keepWaypoint and laststate~=nil then toLineX,toLineY=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,waypointX,waypointY) s.setColor(250, 234, 0, T) s.drawText(2,0,'Dist:'..rnd(mq((ma(waypointX-gpsX)^2)+(ma(waypointY-gpsY)^2)),0)..'m') end drawPosition(w/2,h/2,a) x=w/2 y=h/2 elseif touchscreen then toLineX, toLineY=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,gpsX,gpsY) x=toLineX y=toLineY s.setColor(250,234,0,T) s.drawText(5,0,''..rnd(mq((ma(mapX-gpsX)^2)+(ma(mapY-gpsY)^2)),0)..'m') end if touchscreen or keepWaypoint and laststate~=nil then screen.setColor(250,234,0,T) screen.drawLine(w/2,h/2,toLineX,toLineY) end rcx,rcy=map.screenToMap(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,x,y) s.setColor(0, 150, 0, T) s.drawText(4,h-5,50-rnd(zoom,1)..'x') s.setColor(0,150,0, T) s.drawCircle(w-9,h-9,9) s.drawCircle(w-9,9,9) s.drawTriangleF(w-9,0,w-15,15,w-3,15) s.setColor(155,0,0, T) s.drawText(w-11,9,'N') wdx=w-9+9*mc(wd) wdy=h-9+9*ms(wd) s.drawLine(wdx,wdy,w-9,h-9) if rClean then C=nil c=0 end if rToggle then rla=(ra*mp*2)-(a*mp*2) rx1=gpsX+5000*mc(rla) ry1=gpsY+5000*ms(rla) rx11,ry11=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx1,ry1) rx2=gpsX+5000*mc(rla+0.15) ry2=gpsY+5000*ms(rla+0.15) rx21,ry21=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx2,ry2) rx3=gpsX+5000*mc(rla+0.3) ry3=gpsY+5000*ms(rla+0.3) rx31,ry31=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx3,ry3) rx4=gpsX+5000*mc(rla+0.45) ry4=gpsY+5000*ms(rla+0.45) rx41,ry41=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx4,ry4) s.setColor(0,255,0,10) s.drawCircle(x,y,mq((ma(x-rx11)^2)+(ma(y-ry11)^2))) s.setColor(0,255,0,50) s.drawTriangleF(x,y,rx21,ry21,rx11,ry11) s.setColor(0,255,0,20) s.drawTriangleF(x,y,rx21,ry21,rx31,ry31) s.setColor(0,255,0,10) s.drawTriangleF(x,y,rx41,ry41,rx31,ry31) s.setColor(0,255,0) s.drawLine(x,y,rx11,ry11) if C==nil then C={} c=0 end c=c+1 if c-tn>=10 then c=0 end if rd==0 then C[c]={q='e',w='e'} else ox1=gpsX+rd*mc(rla) oy1=gpsY+rd*ms(rla) C[c]={q=ox1,w=oy1} end dOb() end drawPosition(x,y,a) end function dOb() for i,oc in pairs(C) do if oc.q~='e' and oc.w~='e' then ocx,ocy=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,oc.q,oc.w) g=255-(c-i) s.setColor(255,0,0,g) s.drawCircleF(ocx,ocy,1) end end end function drawPosition(posx,posy,posa) if not iPIR(posx,posy,0,0,w,h) then cx=w-9 cy=27 s.setColor(0, 150, 0,T) s.drawCircle(cx,cy,9) posx=cx posy=cy end bla=(posa*math.pi*2) x1=posx+(-5)*mc(bla) y1=posy+(-5)*ms(bla) x2=posx+(-5)*mc(bla-10) y2=posy+(-5)*ms(bla-10) x3=posx+(-5)*mc(bla+10) y3=posy+(-5)*ms(bla+10) s.setColor(0, 150, 0, T) s.drawTriangleF(x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3) end function onTouch(toggleId) if toggleId==1 then touchscreen=true elseif toggleId==0 then touchscreen=false end end function rnd(num,nDP) local mult=10^(nDP or 0) return math.floor(num*mult+0.5)/mult end function iPIR(x,y,rectX,rectY,rectW,rectH) return x>rectX and y>rectY and x<rectX+rectW and y<rectY+rectH end

function onTick() up = input.getBool(2) down = input.getBool(3) if zoom==nil then zoom=17 end zoomspeed=zoom/170 if zoom>0 and down then zoom=zoom-zoomspeed elseif zoom<50 and up then zoom=zoom+zoomspeed end output.setNumber(1, zoom) end

function inRect(x, y, rectx, recty, rectw, recth) -- checks if click is inside button return x>rectx and y>recty and x<rectw+rectx and y<recth+recty end

rps<mrps*0.75 then screen.setColor(100, 100, 100-255*(rps-0.5*mrps)/(0.25*mrps)) else screen.setColor(255, 255-255*(rps-0.75*mrps)/(0.25*mrps), 0) end for i=1, 36*rps/mrps do -- rps indication screen.drawRectF(b/2+r, a/2+5.5+r, 4, -2*(r-0.5)*temp/120) -- temp indication screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) for i=0, 36, 1 do screen.drawLine(b/2-3+Si(i)*r, a/2+5-Co(i)*r, b/2-3+Si(i+1)*r, screen.drawTextBox(w-30, a/2-r+15, 29, 7, "GEN:", 0, -1) if inp[17]<100 then gen=math.ceil(inp[17]*100-0.5)/100 else gen=math.ceil(inp[17]*10-0.5)/10 end if math.fmod(gen*100, 10)==0 and inp[17]<100 then txt2="0" else txt2="" end if gen<10 then txt1="0" else txt1="" end screen.drawTextBox(w-30, a/2-r+21, 29, 7, txt1..gen..txt2, 0, -1) end
function Co(x) return math.cos(10*x*math.pi/180) end
function Si(x) return math.sin(10*x*math.pi/180) end
